PODCAST SUMMARY HOUR 1:

Defund the police movement led to record increase in murders. Mayorkas: Jan. 6th selfie takers are biggest homeland threat. Psaki won't say how many Haitians have been released into the country. Biden in 1994: It wouldn't matter if Haiti sunk into the sea. Psaki blames Boris Johnson for calling on press without telling her in advance.
